Class Faculty

java.lang.Object
Faculty
public class Faculty extends Object
Represents a faculty in an educational institution. A faculty is associated with a name, department, and a list of module codes.
Version:
(3.0)
Author:
(Adam Fogarty, 22367748);(Aron Calvert, 22370374)
